{"about_the_game":"In this game you have to overcome your fears.<br />\r\nMonsters from under the bed, monsters who knock on doors, knock out windows, cemetery, bugs, spiders, aliens and much more.<br />\r\nAll that you are afraid of, you will find in this game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nUsing the keyboard and mouse, you have to control a character who wears glasses and find out his story by going to the end<br />\r\nWhy does he wake up in a house full of horrors, why does he sleep with glasses, you will learn all this when you reach the end of the game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can open doors with the Q key.<br />\r\nOpen, close your eyes to the E key.<br />\r\nDrag or destroy items by pressing the left mouse button.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the left glass of the glasses, hints will appear at what moment which key will need to be used.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe longer your eyes are open, the longer they will be closed.<br />\r\nIf your eyes are closed for a long time, you will die of fear.<br />\r\nIf your eyes are open at the wrong moment, you will be killed by a monster.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will have to carefully consider each step, when to open your eyes, when to close, in order to survive.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"q","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1794740/291fb8f1732820098ec351ca0f9525e6288b4dde.jpg"},{"name":"w","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1794740/2a03704307506f86341c5f6f754195cfd2ad3697.jpg"},{"name":"e","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1794740/2b8ff7e7abf938bdc9c2d1f60f193a4477d47fd6.jpg"},{"name":"r","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1794740/399ca4ec7764a90ed7349e394e4572fe5b3853cd.jpg"},{"name":"t","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1794740/8abed05129ae4059155f0c8f2095211ac84aed20.jpg"},{"name":"y","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamst